Inventory Management System
=============================

This project is a role-based e-commerce management system that includes three types of users ‚Äî Customer, Seller, and Admin.

Sellers can add products to the platform and manage incoming orders. They can view customer details for each order and choose to either deliver or cancel the order.

Customers can browse products, place orders, and track their purchases.

Admins have complete control over the system. They can delete any user (customer or seller), remove products they find inappropriate, and monitor platform activities. Additionally, admins can view detailed reports for each seller, including sales performance and category-based reports to analyze product trends.

=========================================================================================================================

Tech Stack 
============

Backend : Node.js , express.js
DB : Mongo DB ans SQL

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

