API End Point :-

customer
========

sign up:- http://localhost:3000/api/user/signup
login :- http://localhost:3000/api/user/login
customers details :- http://localhost:3000/api/customer/create
update customers details :- http://localhost:3000/api/customer/:id
product filters:- http://localhost:3000/api/product/all?category=Electronics
filter with pagenation :- http://localhost:3000/api/product/all?page=1&limit=3&minPrice=5000&maxPrice=60000&category=Electronics
search api :- GET http://localhost:3000/api/product/all?search=phone
ordering product :- http://localhost:3000/api/order/create
to see the order products :- http://localhost:3000/api/order/user
to cancel the order :- http://localhost:3000/api/order/cancel
can delete the customer :- http://localhost:3000/api/user/users/delete


seller 
=======

seller details:-  http://localhost:3000/api/seller/create
update the seller details :- http://localhost:3000/api/seller/update/:id
delete the seller account :- http://localhost:3000/api/seller/delete/
product creation :- http://localhost:3000/api/product/create
product details update :- http://localhost:3000/api/product/PROD-e797b7f0
delete the product :- http://localhost:3000/api/product/delete/PROD-e797b7f0
order statuse update :- http://localhost:3000/api/order/update/:order_id
seller can cancle the order :- http://localhost:3000/api/cancel/:order_id


admin :- 

update the admin details :- http://localhost:3000/api/user/users/update
get all users :- http://localhost:3000/api/user/all
get customer details :- http://localhost:3000/api/customer/
get seller details :- http://localhost:3000/api/seller/all
can delete the seller :- http://localhost:3000/api/seller/delete/:id
can delete the cutomer :- http://localhost:3000/api/customer/:id
can delete the product :- http://localhost:3000/api/product/delete/:product_id
admin can delete his onwn id :- http://localhost:3000/api/user/users/delete
admin can create the categories :- http://localhost:3000/api/category/add
get the report of the seller according to seller : - http://localhost:3000/api/order/sell/report
get the report according to category :- http://localhost:3000/api/order/cat/report



üîê Authentication System
=======================
I implemented tow types of authentication systems:-
1. JWT Token Based Authentication
2. Role based Authentication

‚öôÔ∏è Core Functionalities:-
======================
- User Registration and Login
- Role-Based Access Control
- Product Management by Sellers
- Order Management
- Admin Controls and Reporting
- Secure Password Handling with Bcrypt
- Environment Configuration with Dotenv
- Database Interaction using Mongoose and MySQL2
- Session Management with Cookies
- Unique Identifier Generation with UUID
- Development Workflow Automation with Nodemon
